4. Course attribution

   This project originated from the RAS 598: Space Robotics and AI course
   assignment "Rocky Times Challenge - Search, Map, and Analyze."

   This repository reorganizes, documents, and reproduces the working ROS 2 /
   PX4 implementation as a standalone project while preserving academic and
   course attribution.

